<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>Email Verification</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 50px auto;
            background: #ffffff;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }

        .header {
            text-align: center;
            padding-bottom: 20px;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #e5e5e5;
        }

        .header h1 {
            margin: 0;
            color: #333;
        }

        .content {
            margin-top: 20px;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #555;
        }

        .otp-code {
            display: block;
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #333;
            padding: 15px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            background-color: #f9f9f9;
            border: 1px dashed #ccc;
            border-radius: 4px;
        }

        .timestamp {
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #888;
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 10px;
        }

        .footer {
            margin-top: 30px;
            font-size: 12px;
            text-align: center;
            color: #999;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="container">
    <div class="header">
        <h1>Email Verification</h1>
    </div>
    <div class="content">
        <p>Hello {{name}}</p>
        <p>Thank you for registering with us. To verify your email address, please use the following OTP code</p>
        <div class="otp-code">{{otpCode}}</div>
        <p>This code will expire at <strong>{{expiryTime}}</strong>. Please complete the verification process before it
            expires.</p>
        <p>If you did not request this, please ignore this email</p>
        <p>Best regards</p>
        <div class="timestamp">Email generated on <strong>{{timestamp}}</strong></div>
    </div>
    <div class="footer">
        <p>&copy; {{year}} <strong><em>Notes</em></strong>. All rights reserved.</p>
    </div>
</div>
</body>
</html>
